title: Lizbeth Ángeles
text:
Lizbeth Ángeles Mercado (born 29 June 1990), is a Mexican <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> who currently plays for <a href="C.F.%20Pachuca%20%28women%29">Pachuca</a> of the <a href="Liga%20MX%20Femenil">Liga MX Femenil</a>.
Prior to turning professional, Ángeles captained Mexico's team at the 2015 edition of the <a href="Homeless%20World%20Cup">Homeless World Cup</a>. She later worked for the <a href="Federal%20Police%20%28Mexico%29">Federal Police</a> before she joined Pachuca in 2017.
